   Controlled Zone Inlet,1,BLOCK TWO STOREY STOREY 1,BLOCK TWO STOREY STOREY 1 IDEAL LOADS SUPPLY INLET,Undefined,N/A
   Controlled Zone Return,1,BLOCK TWO STOREY STOREY 1,BLOCK TWO STOREY STOREY 1 RETURN OUTLET
