   Controlled Zone Inlet,1,BLOCK ONE STOREY STOREY 0,BLOCK ONE STOREY STOREY 0 IDEAL LOADS SUPPLY INLET,Undefined,N/A
   Controlled Zone Return,1,BLOCK ONE STOREY STOREY 0,BLOCK ONE STOREY STOREY 0 RETURN OUTLET
